Banking application

We want to build a banking application which will allow users to create account, transact using that account and fetch details fo their account
    User
        -Add, edit, delete user
        -Save user details - name, address, contact
        -Assign account number to user
        -fetch user details -  do this
        -fetch bank balance
        -should be able to transact- add or withdraw money
        -fetch average account balance among accounts
        -fetch all accounts having balance > 10000
        -fetch all account having address "pune"
    Bank Account
        -Type of bank account(Savings/Current)
        -Save bank balance of each user
        -Total transaction history of an user
        -Open or close account of a user
        -fetch the bank balance of a user

    Transactions
        -User should be able to do transactions - add or withdraw money
        -Check history of last 10 transactions(mini-statement)

